Name: Building
Description: Physical assets that include offices, data centers, and warehouse facilities.

Name: General
Description: General category for non-building and non-vehicle-sources, which includes Scope 3 travel sources.

Name: Vehicle
Description: Automotive assets that include company cars, company trucks, corporate aircraft, and other fleet vehicles.

Name: Data Center Facility
Description: Report total emissions for data centers and other facilities dominated by IT infrastructure (Scope 1 and 2)

Name: Commercial Building
Description: Report total emissions for commercial buildings (Scope 1 and 2)

Name: Travel
Description: Report total emissions for business travel sources (Scope 3)

Name: Vehicles
Description: Report total emissions for organization-owned and/or operated vehicles, including aircraft (Scope 1)

Name: CBECS
Description: Commercial Buildings Energy Consumption Survey (CBECS) data for U.S. buildings only

Name: Conversion Factors
Description: Conversion factors and global warming potential (GWP) values

Name: Refrigerants
Description: Refrigerant global warming potential (GWP) values

Name: Scope 3 Travel
Description: Emissions factors associated with business travel activities

Name: Air Travel
Description: Use for company business travel on commercial aircraft

Name: Data Center Facility
Description: Use for data centers or facilities dominated by IT use

Name: Fleet Vehicle
Description: Use for vehicles that are owned and/or operated by the company (Scope 1 emissions)

Name: Ground Travel
Description: Use for company business travel in personal cars, trains, taxis and limousines.

Name: Hotel Stay
Description: Use for hotel stays associated with company business travel

Name: Private Jet
Description: Use for travel on aircraft that are owned and/or operated by the company (Scope 1 emissions)

Name: Commercial Building
Description: Use as a generic category for buildings

Name: Rental Car
Description: Use for company business travel in rented cars

Name: VER
Description: Voluntary Emission Reduction - External
